  <entry>
    <title>关于layer调用子窗口的内容</title>
    <url>/2020/06/02/%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8Elayer%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8%E5%AD%90%E7%AA%97%E5%8F%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">btn: [<span class="string">'同步未同步目录'</span>, <span class="string">'关闭'</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    btnAlign: <span class="string">'c'</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        yes: <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> (<span class="params">index, layero</span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            layer.msg(<span class="string">'同步后的数据不可在修改,你确定要同步吗?'</span>, &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                time: <span class="number">0</span> <span class="comment">//不自动关闭</span></span><br><span class="line">                , <span class="attr">btn</span>: [<span class="string">'确定'</span>, <span class="string">'取消'</span>]</span><br><span class="line">                , <span class="attr">yes</span>: <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> (<span class="params">index</span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    layer.close(index);</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">var</span> dataj = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                        qzNo: data.qzNo,</span><br><span class="line">                        acceptanceNo:data.acceptanceNo</span><br><span class="line">                    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//这里的yes:function()&#123;&#125;是父窗口的操作 不能干预到子窗口， 想父窗口进行完操作刷新子窗口怎么做呢？</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//需要获取子窗口的对象</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<p>解决方法:</p>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//这是在上面yes:function()&#123;&#125;方法体里面的ajax请求</span></span><br><span class="line">$.bdy.ajax(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    url:url,</span><br><span class="line">    data:dataj,</span><br><span class="line">    type:<span class="string">"post"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    dataType:<span class="string">"json"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    success:<span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params">result</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">    </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        layer.closeAll(<span class="string">"loading"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(result.flag)</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            layer.msg(result.msg);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">//调用子窗口的refreshTable()方法</span></span><br><span class="line">            $(layero).find(<span class="string">"iframe"</span>)[<span class="number">0</span>].contentWindow.refreshTable()</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            layer.msg(result.msg);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">//调用子窗口的refreshTable()方法</span></span><br><span class="line">            $(layero).find(<span class="string">"iframe"</span>)[<span class="number">0</span>].contentWindow.refreshTable()</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//主要的是$(layero).find("iframe")[0].contentWindow获取子窗口 + 子页面方法名</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      <tags>
        <tag>bug</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
